        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "The Graph sidebar button changes the Bid Center to Graph Mode. The Graph button is only available when in Internal Mode. Graphs split your current Bid into three Parts:"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Cost -  The Cost item represents your Cost as defined by the active Rate Table(s)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Tax -  The Tax item represents the Tax on the Job."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Profit -  The Profit item represents your Profit on the Job as defined by the Markup used for the Job."
        },
        {
